casebody.data:
Office of Disciplinary Counsel v. Christ.

[Cite as Disciplinary Counsel v. Christ (1996), 74 Ohio St.3d 308.]

(No. 95-1670 Submitted September 27, 1995 Decided January 17, 1996.) *309Geoffrey Stem, Disciplinary Counsel, and Lori J. Brown, Assistant Disciplinary Counsel, for relator. Mary L. Cibella, for respondent. Per Curiam.

Upon review of the record, we concur in the board’s finding of misconduct and its recommendation. Respondent is therefore publicly reprimanded for having violated DR 9-101(A). Costs taxed to respondent.

Judgment accordingly.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Wright, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer and Cook, JJ., concur.
